    <lb n="33"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">π</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ρὰ</supplied> Κλαυδίο<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">υ Τερε</supplied>ντιανοῦ <add place="supralinear">υἱοῦ</add> <expan>λε<ex cert="high">γιῶνος</ex></expan> <expan>στρα<ex cert="high">τιώτου</ex></expan>. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.27089" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.27089" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="125" notBefore="101" type="textDate">frühes II</date></p></div><div n="meta.27089" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Gehört zum Tiberianus - Archiv. Neuedition: Strassi, L’archivio di Claudius Tiberianus, 11 (S. 46-49); zur Datierung vgl. ebenda, S. 79-97.</p></div><div n="meta.27089" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Mich.</title><biblScope type="volume">8</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">476</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">27089</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0163</series>; <biblScope type="volume">8</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">476</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0163;8;476" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.27089" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">215</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.27089" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="il